This paper is about image denoising using a convolutional neural network, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of class-aware denoising, which involves incorporating semantic class information into the denoising process, which is related to machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also mentions enhancing textures, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the performance of the denoiser, which is related to optimization and neural networks (cs.NE).
